        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\n(5 comments)\n\nI suggest using PropertyConfiguration with the @Property annotation and eliminating (or replacing) the Property helper classes.  It provides a cleaner interface and eliminates all of the type checking/conversion.  Can find an example of its use in PoolingProperties.",
